data.description: Don't miss this conveniently located home on just under 1/3 of an acre. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1500 square feet, plus a 208 square foot sunroom off the primary bedroom with access to the private backyard patio. This home has radiant floor heat plus a woodstove insert. Updated kitchen has Corian counters, lots of storage and stainless appliances. Double car garage has lots of shelves and workspace. There is room to possibly build an ADU and/or another shop. Plenty of possibilities with this nice home.
